name: Magus Devon is Iconik by dotta

metadata.name: Magus Devon of the Quantum Downs #6001
metadata.description:
Magus Devon of the Quantum Downs specializes in quantum enchanted mushrooms that temporarily grant the ability to perceive alternate realities and, in some cases, those realities have one dimension.

This image is the iconic Magus Devon interpreted as a single 16 pixel line on crimson #1b0400.
